{"tid":132489,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【差佬晒馬】藍絲要立辱警罪 葉劉潑冷水：普通法無以言入罪","createTime":"2017-02-24T00:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T03:17:18.000Z","uid":35790,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ab1c13d171714ba7caecb0cbea9cc8a8ac8eac0b","tid":132489,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T00:56:38.000Z","msg":"【差佬晒馬】藍絲要立辱警罪 葉劉潑冷水：普通法冇以言入罪<br />\n<br />\n2017-02-23 22:06:05 HKT&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n不少警粉和撐警的建制派人士借7警案，再提設立「辱警罪」，不過同屬建制派的保安局前局長葉劉淑儀則唱反調，認為現時已有法例針對傷害公職人員、阻差辦公等，若要為「辱警罪」立法，將非常困難。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">她解釋，「喺普通法入面，係冇以言入罪」，故「辱警罪」難草擬成功，即使立法後，亦難檢控成功。</span></span>她認為政府要多教育社會，提倡公職人員和市民也要文明一些，「唔好咁粗暴」。<br />\n&lt;蘋果&gt;"},{"pid":"977298f95af0fc444620078b660b71c6d144f54b","tid":132489,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T00:58:34.000Z","msg":"好難觸摸呀"},{"pid":"a35a077a1d8356028db33d45c4595d31c836aae9","tid":132489,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T00:59:02.000Z","msg":"近排識講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e92aa0f35951b868f4ac8bd2eb604a96c03f093","tid":132489,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T00:59:44.000Z","msg":"葉局長係無呃你地架"},{"pid":"e72485016bf3f8983f18442b833710056d032435","tid":132489,"uid":34400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:00:39.000Z","msg":"前日去撐警集會今日就潑佢地冷水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb6157780348f7f1be9ab4f34f7e17d06968615","tid":132489,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:02:02.000Z","msg":"包唔包<br />\n網上？內心咒罵 歧視？態度上？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cbe38ee54851889d7b298e3d5b823f27e0eff31","tid":132489,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:03:22.00